images.desc: This is Heritage Hall on level 1. It should be on your right.
This hallway that leads to a pair of elevators should then be on your left.
This is the doorway to University Ave Parking Garage

instructions: Starting on the first floor of McNamara, make your way to the north side of the building where Heritage Hall is.
There will then be elevators to your left (with Heritage Hall on your right), take them down to the lowest level.
You will exit into a study area where you will head in a straight path NW
The end is at the doors labelled University Ave Parking Garage
